naitec_app_title: Controlling with your smartphone is a breeze.
naitec_app_description: Wi-Fi is a convenient solution for smartphone, tablet, and computer users, allowing you to control the air conditioning from anywhere 24 hours a day. Controlling the air conditioning through the app is easy and convenient. The app includes numerous features and a timer, so no additional controllers are needed.
naitec_app_short_description: Wi-Fi is a convenient solution for smartphone, tablet, and computer users, allowing you to control the air conditioning from anywhere 24 hours a day.
effective_heating_description: The ability to heat up to -25 degrees Celsius ensures reliable thermal comfort even on very cold days. The air conditioner is an excellent choice as a source for efficient and cost-effective long-term heating during the cold months. Effective heating with minimal energy costs.
diffuse_cooling_description_1: Diffuse, draft-free cooling is provided by two perforated louvers, which can operate independently, ensuring even cooling without uncomfortable drafts.
diffuse_cooling_description_2: This system is so efficient and comfortable that you can leave it running all night without worrying about drafts, ensuring a peaceful sleep and a pleasant environment throughout the night.
diffuse_cooling_image_description_1: Cools the room quickly and efficiently
coolant_r32_description: The units are very environmentally friendly, thanks in part to the R32 coolant, which is recyclable and can therefore be reused. It also has high efficiency, meaning a 30% lower volume of coolant in the system. Additionally, it boasts low toxicity, which contributes to safe use.
clean_air_description_1: One of the most advanced methods for air purification is the combination of a UVC lamp and ionizer, which helps maintain the highest air quality in your home.
clean_air_description_2: It is highly effective in eliminating pathogens, bacteria, viruses, as well as allergens like dust mites and pollen, while also neutralizing unpleasant odors and other harmful substances.
techinal_parameters_description: Get an overview of all the technical aspects to choose the right air conditioner for your needs.
